title: College baseball scores: No. 9 Texas Tech sweeps No. 3 Oklahoma State to keep Big 12 title hopes alive - NCAA.com
content: College baseball scores: No. 9 Texas Tech sweeps No. 3 Oklahoma State to keep Big 12 title hopes alive  NCAA.com
description: No. 9 Texas Tech defeated No. 3 Oklahoma State, 6-4, on Sunday afternoon to secure a series sweep. Texas Tech now controls its own destiny to win the Big 12 outright.
